<DOCNO> LA112989-0037 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 141151 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 29, 1989, Wednesday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 8; Column 2; Metro Desk 
